{
  "__inputs": [],
  "__requires": [
    {"type": "grafana", "id": "grafana", "name": "Grafana", "version": "10.0.0"},
    {"type": "datasource", "id": "prometheus", "name": "Prometheus", "version": "2.x"}
  ],
  "annotations": {"list": []},
  "description": "Per-tailnet view of an OctraVPN node. Member count + IP allocator utilization land off the WireState snapshot taken at /metrics scrape time; preauth mints/redemptions come from the NodeMetrics counters wired through the MetricsSink trait. Magic-DNS / per-tailnet join-leave rate panels remain TODO because the underlying signals aren't surfaced by the wire layer yet.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [
    {
      "title": "Overview dashboard",
      "type": "dashboards",
      "tags": ["octravpn"],
      "asDropdown": false,
      "includeVars": false,
      "keepTime": true,
      "targetBlank": false
    }
  ],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "row",
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Tailnet membership",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Tailnet members",
      "description": "octravpn_tailnet_member_count — snapshot of `WireState::machines.len()` taken at every /metrics scrape. NOTE: not yet labelled by tailnet_id (single tailnet per node today); per-tailnet labels would require carrying the id through `MachineRegistry`.",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 1},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "octravpn_tailnet_member_count",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance}}",
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"}
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}]},
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "IP allocator utilization",
      "description": "octravpn_ip_allocator_used / octravpn_ip_allocator_capacity. Used mirrors member count today (every machine consumes one IP); capacity is the static `TailnetIpAllocator::host_capacity()` of the CGNAT /10 slice.",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 1},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "octravpn_ip_allocator_used / octravpn_ip_allocator_capacity",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance}} utilization",
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"}
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 0.5},
              {"color": "red", "value": 0.9}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percentunit"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "id": 10,
      "title": "Tailnet activity",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 7},
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "TODO — member join / leave rate",
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Counters to add to `NodeMetrics`:\n\n- `tailnet_member_joins_total{tailnet_id}`\n- `tailnet_member_leaves_total{tailnet_id}`\n\nIncrement at the `WireState` register/unregister entry points. Then plot `rate(...[5m])` here."
      },
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "TODO — magic-DNS query rate",
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Magic-DNS is **not implemented** on the OctraVPN control plane today (see `docs/tailscale-interop-blocker.md`). Once the DNS responder lands, expose `tailnet_magicdns_queries_total{tailnet_id,result}` and plot `rate(...[5m])` partitioned by `result=hit|miss|nxdomain`."
      },
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "id": 20,
      "title": "Preauth surface (currently un-instrumented)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 14},
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Preauth mints & redemptions /s",
      "description": "rate(octravpn_preauth_mints_total[5m]) is bumped at every successful POST /admin/preauth. rate(octravpn_preauth_redemptions_total[5m]) is bumped by the headscale-api wire register handler via the MetricsSink trait. Not yet labelled by tailnet_id (single-tailnet bridge).",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 15},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(octravpn_preauth_mints_total[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance}} mint",
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"}
        },
        {
          "expr": "rate(octravpn_preauth_redemptions_total[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance}} redeem",
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"}
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {"lineInterpolation": "linear", "fillOpacity": 10},
          "unit": "ops"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "id": 30,
      "title": "Wire-protocol health (placeholder)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 21},
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Node uptime (sanity)",
      "description": "Same series as the overview dashboard; included here so a tailnet operator can confirm the node serving their tailnet is up.",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 22},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "octravpn_uptime_seconds",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance}}",
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"}
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit": "s", "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}]}}
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Sessions on this instance",
      "description": "octravpn_active_sessions — proxy for tailnet activity until per-tailnet metrics land.",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 22},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "octravpn_active_sessions",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance}}",
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"}
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit": "short", "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "yellow", "value": 5000}, {"color": "red", "value": 9000}]}}
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      }
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "style": "dark",
  "tags": ["octravpn", "tailnet"],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "tailnet_id",
        "type": "custom",
        "label": "Tailnet ID (placeholder — no metric labelled by tailnet_id is exposed yet)",
        "query": "octravpn-interop",
        "current": {"text": "octravpn-interop", "value": "octravpn-interop"},
        "includeAll": false,
        "multi": false
      }
    ]
  },
  "time": {"from": "now-6h", "to": "now"},
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "",
  "title": "OctraVPN — Tailnet",
  "uid": "octravpn-tailnet",
  "version": 1,
  "weekStart": ""
}
